@colonia_proletaria
title: La colonia proletaria
subtitle: The invasion method, taught: surveyors, lists, and speed — a neighborhood born in one night.
card-image: img/medrano.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; sup_colonos += 4; colonia_presion += 1; expediente += 3

His people teach yours the craft with the pride of artisans: the land scouted by day, the families organized by manzana, the stakes and cardboard moving in the dark, and by dawn a thousand homesteads that the law would need a small war to reverse — which is precisely the calculation. Where the method takes root, the colonos learn the lesson under the lesson: the city they were promised can be taken, lot by lot, by people holding hands in a line at sunrise.

