title: La autodefensa del barrio
subtitle: [? if via = "armada" : The colonia as the urban war's shore — recruits, safe houses, a population that does not see. ?][? if via = "politica" or via = "institucional" : The colonia holds its ground: pickets against the granaderos, the eviction made too expensive to order. ?]
